TransmissionModes

julia> using EnergyModelsGeography
julia> const EMG = EnergyModelsGeography 
julia> using AbstractTrees
julia> AbstractTrees.children(x::Type) = subtypes(x)

julia> print_tree(EMG.TransmissionMode)
TransmissionMode
├─ PipeMode
│  ├─ PipeLinepackSimple
│  └─ PipeSimple
├─ RefDynamic
└─ RefStatic

The leaf nodes of the above type hierarchy tree are structs, while the inner vertices are abstract types. The individual nodes and their fields are explained in the public library.
